PSI: Use a psionic power

Syntax: psi <power> [at <target>]
        psi <power> <target>

DESCRIPTION:
  Activate a known psionic power. Each power costs ISP. In combat, using
  psi costs one attack from your APM pool.

  Examples:
    psi telepathy at guard
    psi mind block
    psi telekinesis at crate
    psi bio-regeneration

NOTES:
  You must have psionic access through your race or OCC.
  Type help psionics for a list of common powers and ISP costs.
  Several powers also have shortcut commands (telepathy, telekinesis, etc.).

SEE ALSO: psionics, meditate, abilities, score
